==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Whetter
<hw>Whet"ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>One who, or that which, whets, sharpens, or
stimulates.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A tippler; one who drinks whets.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Steele.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Whettlebones</ent>⟦br⟧
